<h1>Save 100 million lives from cardiovascular disease</h1>

<p class="intro">More than 18 million people die from cardiovascular disease each year, with a majority of these premature deaths occurring in low- and middle-income countries. Proven, scalable solutions exist, but there has been little investment and little progress made so far.</p>

