        <h3>Hypertension control</h3>
        <p>High blood pressure kills more people than all infectious diseases combined. Yet, there are simple, proven, affordable solutions that can be done within existing healthcare systems &#8212; for as little as $1 per person each year.</p>
    </div>
    
