<p>The world is in the midst of a momentous shift in its approach to healthcare. We now recognize that the number of people dying from chronic diseases far outnumbers deaths from infectious diseases. Providers and governments are shifting their focus from preventing infections to preventing cardiovascular disease, and Resolve to Save Lives is accelerating that shift.</p>

<h2>How we work </h2>
<p>We work closely with partners, governments and civil society to help countries improve the heart health of their citizens. We work directly with countries, or through our partners, to fund and develop customized cardiovascular disease prevention programs based on the most recent evidence-based practices.</p>

